## API Key Management

- All API keys in environment variables — never in code or Convex DB
- Validated at app startup — crash loudly if missing in production
- Rotation: all keys must be rotatable without code changes
- Never log API keys — Sentry scrubs sensitive fields

```typescript
// ✅ Startup validation
const requiredEnvVars = [
  "ELEVENLABS_API_KEY",
  "DEEPGRAM_API_KEY",
  "ANTHROPIC_API_KEY",
  "POLAR_WEBHOOK_SECRET",
  "HUBSPOT_CLIENT_SECRET",
]
requiredEnvVars.forEach(key => {
  if (!process.env[key]) throw new Error(`Missing required env var: ${key}`)
})
```

