## Rate Limiting

Apply rate limiting on these routes to prevent abuse:

| Route | Limit |
|---|---|
| `POST /api/interview/start` | 5 starts per token per hour |
| `GET /interview/[token]` | 30 requests per IP per minute |
| `POST /api/content/generate` | 10 generations per workspace per hour |
| `POST /api/hubspot/push` | 20 pushes per workspace per hour |

Use Vercel's built-in rate limiting or `@upstash/ratelimit` with Upstash Redis.

