## GDPR Compliance

### Data Collected

| Data | Source | Stored | Purpose |
|---|---|---|---|
| Workspace user email | Clerk | Convex | Auth, notifications |
| Guest name (optional) | Interview form | Convex | Context only |
| Guest email (optional) | Interview form | Convex | Thank-you email |
| Interview audio | Deepgram stream | Cloudflare R2 | Transcript generation |
| Interview transcript | Deepgram/Claude | Convex | Content generation |
| HubSpot OAuth tokens | OAuth flow | Convex | CRM integration |

### Guest Data Rules (GDPR)
- Guests are informed of recording **before** interview starts — consent screen required
- Consent logged with timestamp in `interviews` table
- Guests can request deletion — audio and transcript deleted on request
- Guest data never shared with third parties beyond processing (Deepgram, Anthropic)
- Deepgram called with `diarize=false` for single-speaker interviews — minimal data

### Data Processing Agreements
Required DPAs with:
- Anthropic (Claude API)
- Deepgram (STT)
- ElevenLabs (TTS)
- Convex (Database)
- Cloudflare (R2 Storage)

### Data Residency
- Convex deployment: EU region preferred for Norwegian/European customers
- R2 bucket: EU region (`eu-west-1` or `eu-central-1`)
- Deepgram: EU endpoint (`api.eu.deepgram.com`) when processing EU interviews

### Retention Policy
- Audio recordings: deleted after 90 days (R2 lifecycle rule)
- Transcripts: retained while workspace is active; deleted on workspace cancellation + 30 days
- User data: deleted within 30 days of account deletion request
- Credit transaction ledger: retained 7 years (financial records requirement)

---

## What Never to Do

- ❌ Never log interview transcripts to console or Sentry breadcrumbs
- ❌ Never store raw audio in Convex — R2 only
- ❌ Never return another workspace's data — always filter by `workspaceId`
- ❌ Never expose HubSpot access/refresh tokens to the client
- ❌ Never skip webhook signature verification (Polar, HubSpot)
- ❌ Never use guest token as plain text in DB — always hash before storing
- ❌ Never allow credits to go negative without blocking the action
- ❌ Never collect guest PII beyond what the brief requires
